    "• Click a direction to start walking.\n• By default, it takes 100 steps to walk a tile.\n• If you stop and change direction, your step count resets.\n• You may get into an encounter.": "•点击一个方向开始行走。\n•默认情况下，移动一个地块需要100步。\n•如果您停止并改变方向，您的步数将重置。•你可能会遇到麻烦。",
    "• Click the Abilities button to open the menu.\n• Abilities are divided into Active and Passive types.\n  • If you have enough AP, you can unlock an Ability.\n• There is no limit to the number of Active Abilities you can equip.\n• Too many? Feel free to unequip some for clarity.\n• You’re limited to two passives at a time, so choose wisely.": "•点击技能按钮打开菜单。技能分为主动和被动两种。如果你有足够的技能点（AP），你可以解锁一个技能。你可以装备的主动技能数量没有限制。太多了？为了清楚起见，你可以卸下一些装备。你同时最多只能使用两个被动技能，所以要明智地选择。",
    "• Combat happens automatically when you're attacked.\n• Equipped Passive Abilities trigger with your attacks.\n• Some Passive Abilities trigger on being damaged or at combat start.\n• This Assassin uses First Strike to attack before anything else.\n• You fight until someone is defeated no running, no escape.\n• (Unless you have an ability or item that allows escape.)": "•当你受到攻击时，战斗会自动发生。装备被动技能与你的攻击一起触发。一些被动技能在被伤害或战斗开始时触发。这个刺客使用第一击在任何其他攻击之前。你要战斗到有人被打败，不要逃跑，不要逃跑。\n•（除非你的技能或物品能让你逃脱）",
    "• Using Abilities is easy.\n• Just click use.\n• Active Abilities can be used in combat or outside of it.\n• Passive Abilities are always active, no need to click.\n• You can equip or unequip them in the Abilities menu.": "•使用技能很简单。\n•只需点击使用。主动技能可以在战斗中或战斗外使用。被动技能总是主动的，不需要点击。你可以在技能菜单中装备或取消装备它们。",
    "• Using Gear is straightforward.\n  • Open the Gear Screen.\n  • You can can sort by slot.\n  • You can also filter by gear that can be equipped by your current Job.\n  • Just click equip.\n  • Click unequip to remove.\n  • Gear can be used in combat or outside of it.\n  • Changes to Stats are illustrated on the Gear.": "•使用装备很简单。\n•打开装备界面。你可以按栏位排序。\n•也可以根据当前职业可穿戴的装备进行筛选。\n•点击“装备”即可。装备可以在战斗中使用，也可以在战斗之外使用。•属性的变化会在装备上显示。",
    "• Using Items is easy.\n• You can equip two items at a time to your quick slots.\n• You can also use them directly out of the Inventory Screen.\n• Just click the item you want to use.\n• Items can be used in combat or outside of it.": "•使用物品很简单。•你可以一次装备两件物品到你的快捷栏。你也可以直接在库存界面中使用它们。\n•只需点击您要使用的物品。物品可以在战斗中或战斗外使用。",
