    "Choose optional challenge modes for this run. These settings are permanent for this save file. If you don't know what these do, it's recommended to leave them off for your first playthrough.": "选择可选的挑战模式。这些设置对于这个保存文件是永久的。如果你不知道它们的作用，建议你在第一次玩游戏时不要使用它们。",
