    "Lurkers only add +1 to your level cap instead of +3. This will make the game significantly harder. Not recommended for first-time players.": "潜伏者的等级上限只增加+1而不是+3。这将大大增加游戏的难度。不建议首次玩家使用。",
    "New Game — Slot": "新游戏-栏位",
