    "Evasion gives a chance to dodge physical enemy attacks. Higher EVA, slower enemy attacks, and weaker (low-tier) foes make dodging more likely. Stronger (high-tier) enemies are much harder to dodge, and dodge chance is always between": "闪避技能能让你有机会避开敌人的物理攻击。较高的 EVA（闪避值）会使敌人的攻击速度变慢，弱小（低等级）的敌人更容易闪避。强大的（高等级）敌人则更难闪避，而闪避成功的几率始终处于以下区间：",
    "Magic evasion gives a chance to avoid spells and other magical attacks. It follows the same rules as regular evasion: higher MEVA helps more against slower, weaker enemies, and less against fast, high-tier foes. Dodge chance is always between": "魔法闪避机制能增加闪避法术和其他魔法攻击的几率。其规则与常规的规避机制相同：魔法闪避值越高，对速度较慢、力量较弱的敌人越有效，而对速度快、等级较高的敌人则效果较弱。闪避几率始终处于以下范围：",
    "DEF reduces incoming physical damage by": "DEF（防御力）能减少受到的物理伤害。",
    "HP is your current health. Max HP = STA ×": "HP（生命值）是你当前的生命值。最大HP = 耐力值 ×",
    "MP is used for special abilities. Max MP = MAG ×": "MP（魔法值）用于特殊技能。最大MP = 魔法 ×",
    "Some attacks are Accurate and cannot be dodged. In Hoard encounters, EVA is far less effective, so expect to be hit more often.": "有些攻击是准确且无法躲避的。在宝藏遭遇战中，EVA（闪避值）效果较差，所以你可能会更频繁地被攻击。",
    "Some spells are effectively unavoidable. In Hoard encounters, MEVA is far less effective, so magical attacks will land more often.": "有些法术是完全无法闪避的。在宝藏遭遇战中，MEVA（魔法闪避值）效果较差，所以魔法攻击会更频繁地命中。",
    "Stat Growth per Level": "每级的属性增长",
    "Evasion gives a chance to dodge physical enemy attacks. Higher EVA, slower enemy attacks, and weaker (low-tier) foes make dodging more likely. Stronger (high-tier) enemies are much harder to dodge, and dodge chance is always between 5% and 95%.  **Note:** Some attacks are Accurate and cannot be dodged. In Hoard encounters, EVA is far less effective, so expect to be hit more often.": "闪避可以让你有机会闪避敌人的物理攻击。闪避值越高、敌人攻击速度越慢、敌人等级越低，闪避成功的几率就越大。等级越高的敌人越难闪避，闪避几率始终在 5% 到 95% 之间。**注意：**有些攻击是命中型的，无法闪避。在遭遇大量敌人时，闪避的效果会大大降低，所以做好被击中的准备。",
    "Magic evasion gives a chance to avoid spells and other magical attacks. It follows the same rules as regular evasion: higher MEVA helps more against slower, weaker enemies, and less against fast, high-tier foes. Dodge chance is always between 5% and 95%.  **Note:** Some spells are effectively unavoidable. In Hoard encounters, MEVA is far less effective, so magical attacks will land more often.": "魔法闪避（MEVA）使玩家有机会闪避法术和其他魔法攻击。其规则与普通闪避相同：更高的MEVA值对速度较慢、攻击力较低的敌人效果更佳，而对速度较快、等级较高的敌人效果较差。闪避几率始终在5%到95%之间。**注意：**某些法术几乎无法闪避。在遭遇战中，MEVA的效果会大大降低，因此魔法攻击更容易命中目标。",
