    "This feature is experimental and may change or break in future updates.": "此功能为实验性功能，在未来的更新中可能会发生变化或出现故障。",
    "Toggle stat bonuses granted by each golem specialization. Turning a specialization off stops its golems from contributing combat stats, but they still exist for other purposes.": "切换每个魔像专精所提供的属性加成。关闭某个专精会停止其魔像对战斗属性的贡献，但它们仍会出于其他目的而存在。",
    "Toggle whether certain passive skills may automatically consume items during combat. These settings apply per save file.": "调整某些被动技能是否在战斗中自动消耗物品。这些设置针对每个存档文件生效。",
    "Top tiles by lifetime enemy kills this save.": "本次存档中，按敌人终身击杀数排名前几的玩家。",
    "Tweak combat visuals and logs. Disabling these can reduce flashing or improve performance on some devices.": "调整战斗画面和日志。禁用这些功能可以减少闪烁或在某些设备上提高性能。",
    "Unlock survival-oriented passive skills to configure them here.": "解锁以生存为导向的被动技能，并在此处进行配置。",
    "Use lake water automatically when crafting at a lake": "在湖边制作时，自动使用湖水",
    "Useful for promoted jobs, arena farming, or challenge runs.": "适用于晋升职业、竞技场刷分或挑战通关。",
    "Lurkers & Level Cap": "潜伏者 & 等级上限",

    "• Each Lurker you defeat permanently raises your level cap.\n• Some jobs receive special rewards for defeating specific Lurkers.\n• Check your logs, inventory, and gear screens after a Lurker kill.\n• If you didn’t get the job reward, you can refight the Lurker once you’ve built the appropriate Arena tier.\n• If that doesn’t make sense yet, it will later.": "• 每击败一个潜伏者，你的等级上限就会永久提升。\n• 某些职业在击败特定的潜伏者后会获得特殊奖励。\n• 在杀死潜伏者后，请检查你的日志、库存和装备界面。\n• 如果你没有获得职业奖励，那么在建立了相应的竞技场等级后，你可以再次与该潜伏者战斗。\n• 如果现在还不明白这些内容，那以后就会明白了。",
    "• Click a direction to start walking.\n• You can also use WASD or the arrow keys while the compass widget is open \n• Q and E for Item Quick Slots).\n• Spacebar for Weapon Ability\n• 1-9 for Ability Quick Slots.\n• By default, it takes 100 steps to walk a tile.\n• If you stop and change direction, your step count resets.\n• You may get into an encounter.": "• 点击一个方向开始行走。\n• 在指南针浮窗打开时，您也可以使用WASD或箭头键。\n• Q和E用于物品快捷栏。\n• 空格键用于武器技能。\n• 1-9用于技能快捷栏。\n• 默认情况下，行走一格需要100步。\n• 如果您停下并改变方向，步数将重置。\n• 您可能会遭遇敌人。",
