    "You can only change jobs in a Temple.": "只有在圣殿中才能更换职业。",
    "The elder of the town is worried about a missing priest who went to cleanse a nearby temple. The priest has not returned, and the elder fears something terrible has happened. The temple lies east of the Nevergrave, past the blighted ground. The player must find the temple, confront the corrupted priest, and report back to the elder.": "镇上的长者很担心一位去附近圣殿的净化祭司失踪了。祭司尚未归来，长者担心一定发生了可怕的事情。这座圣殿位于永寂归所（Nevergrave）以东，越过那片荒芜的土地。玩家必须找到这座圣殿，与那名被腐化的祭司交涉，并向长者汇报情况。",
