    "[CURSED] This doesn't look very scientific at all, but somehow you make it work with the outfit. 50% chance to afflict the enemy with venom each combat turn. Every second there is a one in 300 chance the necklace will be unequipped. And kill you.": "[诅咒] 这看起来一点也不科学，但不知怎的，你却能让这套装备发挥出效果。每场战斗中都有 50% 的几率使敌人中毒。每秒钟都有 1/300 的几率这枚项链会被取下，然后会置你于死地。",
    "[CURSED] A vest stitched from the rib bones of a Real Wolf. Wearing it makes you feel terrifyingly alive and Real, but the ribs are unstable, and will eventually tear themselves apart. And kill you.": "[诅咒]用真狼的肋骨缝制的背心。穿上它会让你感觉异常地充满活力且真实无比，但这些肋骨并不稳固，最终会自行断裂，从而置你于死地。",
    "[CURSED] A heavy sash made from the Real Grizzly's hide.  It does not make you any wiser, but it does make you a lot harder to knock down.  Increases the Monk multiplier cap to 1000.": "[诅咒]一条用真正灰熊的皮做的沉重腰带。它并不能让你变得更聪明，但确实能让你变得难以被击倒。将武僧倍率上限提升至 1000。",
    "woodAxe": "木斧",
    "woolCoat": "羊毛大衣",
    "A blackened buckler engraved with binding runes.  Forged to turn sorcery aside.": "一块被熏黑的盾牌，上面刻有束缚符文。铸造而成，能驱散魔法。",
    "A cheap bottle with an expensive lesson. On critical hits, it breaks your mind open for twenty seconds.": "一瓶廉价却蕴含昂贵教训的酒。当受到暴击时，它会让你精神崩溃二十秒。",
    "A chitin stiletto, hollowed to a capillary edge.": "一把几丁质细剑，被挖空至毛细管边缘。",
    "A living mask stitched from a healthy set of lungs. It flexes faintly as you breathe.  The right kind of person could probably breathe and even build things underwater with these.": "一个由健康肺组织缝合而成的活体面具。当你呼吸时，它会微微颤动。合适的人或许能借助它在水下呼吸，甚至建造东西。",
    "A mysterious shield radiating with debug energy. +100 EVA": "一个散发着调试能量的神秘护盾。+100 EVA",
    "A parrying dagger wielded in the off-hand for both defense and deception. [Assassin] +5 Strength, +7 Agility, +5 Evasion.": "一把用于防御和欺骗的副手格挡匕首。[刺客] +5力量，+7敏捷，+5闪避。",


    "A shield large enough to hide the peasantry behind.": "一个足够大的盾牌，能将平民百姓掩护其后。",
