    "• Temples unlock Prestige: you can reset your level for permanent growth.\n• Stat growth depends on your current job when you level; gains persist even if you change jobs.\n• You can reset to level 1 and change your job at Temples.\n• Donate fleeting experiences for True Memories to gain permanent stat boosts.\n• Donated experience can sanctify passive skills so they’re permanently equipped.\n• Check the Temple for details.": "• 圣殿可提升声望：您可以重置等级以获得永久提升。\n• 统计值的增长取决于您升级时所从事的职业；即使您更换职业，这些增长也会持续存在。\n• 您可以回到圣殿重置至 1 级，并更换职业。\n• 用短暂的体验进行奉献以获取真实记忆，从而获得永久性的属性加成。\n• 奉献的经验可以赋予被动技能神圣属性，使其永久装备。\n• 请查看圣殿获取详细信息。",
