    "The professor believes Reality is leaking into the world.\nHe demands overwhelming proof. Not theory, not metaphor, but tangible, undeniable evidence.\nBring him the following REAL specimens:\n • 1,000 Bear Skins\n • 1,000 Elephant Skins\n • 1,000 Horse Shoes\n • 1,000 Owl Feathers\n • 1,000 Rabbit Skins\n • 1,000 Raccoon Skins\n • 1,000 Rat Skins\n • 1,000 Real Honeycombs\n • 1,000 Real Raw Fish\n • 1,000 Real Stone\n • 1,000 Real Wood\n • 1,000 Snake Skins\n • 1,000 Weasel Skins\n\nAnd finally:\n • 40 Length": "“教授认为现实正在渗入这个世界。”\n“他要求的是无可辩驳的证据。不是理论，不是隐喻，而是切实的、不容否认的证明。”\n“带给他以下真实的样本：”\n“• 1,000 张熊皮”\n“• 1,000 张象皮”\n“• 1,000 只马蹄铁”\n“• 1,000 根猫头鹰羽毛”\n“• 1,000 张兔皮”\n“• 1,000 张浣熊皮”\n“• 1,000 张鼠皮”\n“• 1,000 份真正的蜂巢”\n“• 1,000 条真正的鱼”\n“• 1,000 块真正的石头”\n“• 1,000 块真正的木头”\n“• 1,000 张蛇皮”\n“• 1,000 张鼬鼠皮”\n“以及最后：”\n“• 40 长度”",
