    "Your current Reality and where your cap comes from.": "查看当前现实值与上限构成来源。",
    "The Scarecrow says he's lonely. He asked you to create a proper crowd of workers, hopefully 30 of each will mollify him.   He seems to have a particular interest in Accountants, so make sure to include those in the mix.": "稻草人说他很孤独。他请求您组建一支合适的员工队伍，希望能有 30 名每种工种的员工，这样或许能让他感到欣慰一些。他似乎对会计人员特别感兴趣，所以一定要将他们纳入其中。",
    "Somehow, this rabbit is real. You've fought \"rabbits\" before, but you can clearly see the difference.  Somehow, this one is alive.   Being around it, you feel so much weaker and more aware of what you actually are.": "不知怎的，这只兔子是真实的。你以前也和“兔子”打过架，但这次你能明显看出它们的不同之处。不知怎的，这只兔子是活生生的。和它在一起，你会感到自己变得如此虚弱，也更加清楚自己到底是什么样的存在。",
    "Build 30 each of the following worker golems: Angler, Forester, Farmer, Mycologist, Papermaker, Scribe, Scrounger, Chef, Miner, Blacksmith, and Accountant. Accountants can help turn your production engine into AP for more golems.": "建造 30 个以下类型的工匠魔像：钓鱼者、伐木工、农夫、真菌学者、造纸匠、文士、拾荒者、厨师、矿工、铁匠和会计。会计可以协助将你的生产系统转换为技能点（AP）以制造更多此类怪兽。",
