    "50 Feather + 50 Big Feather → 1 Gryphon Treat, reduces Gryphon Pet cooldown by around 10%.": "50 羽毛 + 50 大羽毛 → 1 狮鹫口粮，减少狮鹫宠物冷却时间约10%。",
