    "Wizard Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Paladin Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Assassin Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Chemist Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Monk Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Wanderer Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Thief Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Witch Hunter Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Knight Regalia Cache (Drop: 18%), Berserker Tattoo Cache (Drop: 18%)": "巫师盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、圣骑士盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、刺客盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、化学家盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、武僧盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、旅者盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、盗贼盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、猎巫者盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、骑士盛装宝箱（掉落率：18%）、狂战士纹身宝箱（掉落率：18%）",

    "The Iron from the Stones of Mind is not actually real, but we can make it real, for the low price of some of your Memories. You can then use it to infuse your weapons, making them much, much stronger.": "心灵之石中的铁并非真实存在，但我们可以用一些记忆碎片作为代价，将其转化为现实。之后，你可以用它来强化你的武器，使其威力大幅提升。",
    "A shimmering wall of force hums with pressure.   Something powerful lurks just beyond the veil.": "一道闪烁的力场之墙嗡鸣着，涌动着压力。某种强大的力量正潜伏在帷幕之后。",

    "He seems to be writing something in the air, but there's nothing there.\nHe turns to look at you, and you realize perhaps there is nothing anywhere. Just... emptiness.": "他似乎在空中写着什么，但那里什么也没有。\n他转头看向你，你这才意识到，或许这里什么都没有。只有……一片空虚。",

    "No one here seems to know how they got here. Good coffee, though.": "这里似乎没人知道他们自己是怎么到这儿的。不过，咖啡不错。",


