    "\"Your touch has awakened the Web’s true power.\"  \n\n\"Take this fungal spore pendant.\"\n\n\"It will allow you to understand the beauty of Decay, and protect you from its harm.\"": "“你的触碰唤醒了菌网的真正力量。”\n\n“戴上这枚孢子吊坠。”\n\n“它将让你领略腐朽之美，并保护你免受其害。”",

