    "A symbiotic fungus lives within your wounds.\nYou hemorrhage constantly, but your attacks seed enemies with flesh-eating rot.": "共生真菌寄居于你的伤口之中。\n你持续溢血，但你的攻击会向敌人播撒食肉腐烂。",
