    "Paper Obsession": "纸品执念",
    "CYA.  Your Accountant Golems know they need to cover their tracks.": "留好记录。你的会计魔像知道他们需要掩盖痕迹。会计储备池获得",
    "x AP added to the Accounting pool.": "倍 技能点（AP）。",

    "“History will be kind to me for I intend to write it.”\n~ Winston Churchill": "“历史会善待我，因为我将会书写它。”\n~ 温斯顿·丘吉尔",
    "“History will be kind to me for I intend to write it.”": "“历史会善待我，因为我将会书写它。”",
    "~ Winston Churchill": "~ 温斯顿·丘吉尔",
    "As a Scribe, consume 1 Noncombat Scroll and 50M MP to create a Paper Trail for 30 minutes. Your Accountant golems will produce 100x more AP.": "作为文士，消耗 1 张非战斗卷轴与 5000 万法力值，制造持续 30 分钟的“纸迹”效果。此期间，你的会计魔像产出技能点（AP） × 100 倍。",

    "As a Papermaker, consume 1M Blank Scrolls to become a Paper Tiger for 30 minutes. Your stats will be almost nothing. Enemies take 15% of their CURRENT HP per second in damage from your reputation. All reactionaries are paper tigers.": "作为造纸匠，消耗 100 万张空白卷轴，化身“纸老虎”，持续 30 分钟。你的属性将基本归零。但是源于你的威名，敌人每秒会受到当前生命值 15% 的伤害。一切反动派都是纸老虎。",
    "“Paper is to write things down that we need to remember. Our brains are used to think.”\n~ Albert Einstein": "“纸张是用来记录我们需要记住的事情的。我们的大脑是用来思考的。”\n~ 阿尔伯特·爱因斯坦",
    "“Paper is to write things down that we need to remember. Our brains are used to think.”": "“纸张是用来记录我们需要记住的事情的。我们的大脑是用来思考的。”",
