    "Paladin Only: Requires Proving Your Faith. Consume 100 Giga Potions at once, that seems safe. Your flesh is anointed, healing 5% of your max HP every second for 10 minutes. Or maybe it's just an overdose. Status lost on Job Change.": "圣骑士专属：需完成“证汝信仰”。一次性消耗 100 瓶超级药水——听起来很安全。你的躯体受膏，每秒恢复最大生命值 5%，持续 10 分钟。也可能只是一次过量用药。更换职业后状态消失。",
