    "For every 1000 steps taken as a Wanderer, gain +1 flat damage × character level (up to +9999 × character level).": "旅者每走1000步，获得 +1 固定伤害×角色等级（最高 +9999 ×角色等级）。",
    "“For which of you, desiring to build a tower, does not first sit down and count the cost, whether you have enough to complete it?”\n~ Jesus, Luke 14:28": "“你们中间谁想要盖一座楼，不先坐下来计算费用，看看自己有没有足够的钱盖完呢？”\n~ 耶稣，路加福音 14:28",
