    "Consecration of the Cracked Sanctum": "破碎圣所的祝圣",
    "You kneel at the restored altar and speak the old words. The stone answers.\n\nEffect: For 60 minutes, each enemy kill counts as 2 kills toward cleansing progress.\nCooldown: 1 hour.": "你跪在修复后的祭坛前，念诵古老的咒语。石头回应了你。\n\n效果：持续60分钟，每次击杀敌人计为2次净化进度。\n\n冷却时间：1小时。",

    "Vitality of the Spore Sanctum": "孢子圣所的活力",
    "The air blooms with soft light. Your wounds knit faster.\n\nEffect: For 60 minutes, healing from all sources is doubled.\nCooldown: 1 hour.": "空气中弥漫着柔和的光芒。你的伤口愈合得更快了。\n\n效果：持续60分钟，所有来源的治疗效果翻倍。\n\n冷却时间：1小时。",

    "Insight of the Drowned Sanctum": "沉没圣所的洞见",
    "Cold water beads on stone that should be dry.\n\nEffect: For 60 minutes, XP gained is doubled.\nCooldown: 1 hour.": "冰冷的水珠落在应该干燥的石头上。\n效果：持续 60 分钟，获得的经验值翻倍。\冷却时间：1 小时。",

    "Audit of the Atrophic Sanctum": "凋零圣所的结算",
    "You step over scattered ledgers and speak the numbers.\n\nEffect: For 60 minutes, Golem Workshop output is doubled.\nCooldown: 1 hour.": "你跨过散落的账册，念出那些数字。效果：在 60 分钟内，魔像工坊的产出翻倍。冷却时间：1 小时。",

