    "\"You are whole enough.\"  \n\n\"The spores will sleep.\"": "“你已经足够完整了。”  \n\n“孢子将会沉睡。”",

    "A warning about circles and copies has reached you. Something is moving out beyond.": "你已收到关于圆环和复制品的警告。有什么东西正在向外扩散。",
    "The path begins where someone tried to measure a circle by its edge. The First Half of the First Four.  From what you remember about Pi, the first four digits are 3.141, so the first half of that is 3.1.": "这条路始于有人试图测量圆周率。前四位数字的前半部分。根据你对圆周率的记忆，它的前四位数字是 3.141，所以它的前半部分是 3.1。",
    "No response for this topic.": "这个话题没有更多消息了。",

    "Mine your way into Collapsed Dreams (-3,0) and speak with the Night Owl.": "挖开通往崩塌的梦境（-3,0）的道路，与猫头鹰交谈。",
    "Find the Troll Hole (4,-1).": "找到巨魔巢穴 (4,-1).",
    "It looked like he paid out for a lot of areas, maybe you could get some helpful gear clearing other dungeons too.": "看起来他愿意为很多地方付钱，也许清理其他地牢也能获得一些有用的装备。",
    "Perhaps that one North of Spore, if you could pick the lock on the gate in town.": "或许可以去孢子镇北边的那个地方，前提是你得能撬开镇上大门的锁。",

    "I serve at the shrine. \n\nMy duty is to heal the weary.": "“我侍奉于神龛。”\n\n“我的职责是治愈疲惫之人。”",
    "\"Heard some chemist’s figured out how to turn slime and dirty water into gold.\" \n\n\"Don’t ask how.\"": "“听说有些化学家已经找到了把粘液和污水变成黄金的方法。”\n\n“别问我他们是怎么做到的。”",
    "\"The old beasts don’t just guard their dens, they judge you by which you you happen to be at the moment.\"\n\n\"Come with purpose to the forest, or wander there.\"  \n\n\"The lake listens, and you might spend a lot of time fishing there, but you might also be the kind to spend a lot of time drinking swamp sludge.\"  \n\n\"I don't judge.\"  \n\n\"Some people are a lot like ghosts, you know.\"  \n\n\"Sometimes all I need to clear the ghosts is a good meal.\"": "“那些老东西不只是看窝，它们还会打量你——看你这会儿是哪个你。”\n\n“要么带着目的进林子，要么就随便逛逛。”\n\n“湖会听的。你可能花很多时间在那儿钓鱼，但也可能你是那种花很多时间喝沼泽泥水的人。”\n\n“我不管这些。”\n\n“有些人呐，跟鬼魂似的，你知道吧。”“有时候，赶走那些鬼魂，一顿好饭就够了。”",
    "\"Back already?\" \n\n\"Let’s see… yep, that’s 10 slime balls.\" \n\n\"Good work.\"": "“这么快就回来了？”\n\n“让我看看……嗯，是10个粘液球。”\n\n“干得好。”",
    "No spells available for": "没有可用的法术关于",

    "Acolyte Rynn believes concentrated Slime Essence can help stem the corruption. Gather ten vials and return to her at your home.": "辅祭琳恩相信浓缩的史莱姆精华可以阻止腐化。收集十瓶，然后带回家交给她。",
    "Unlocks the Paladin job.": "解锁圣骑士职业。",
    "The hunter wants proof the river horror bleeds. Bring him eight of its tentacles.": "猎人想要证明河中怪物也会流血。给他带八条它的触手来。",
    "Hint: unlocking": "提示：解锁",
    "is one way to start making Blank Golems.": "是开始制造空白魔像的途径之一",
    "Someday you will have an army...": "总有一天，你会拥有一支军队…",

    "No temple has been built at this location.": "此地尚未建造圣殿。",
    "Construct a Home Temple here to access temple features. (Requires Mason job)": "在此处建造家园圣殿以解锁圣殿功能。（需要石匠职业）",
    "Required Inputs": "所需材料",
