    "Sometimes the only thing you want to wear is yourself.": "有时你唯一想穿的，就是你自己。",
    "Tailoring lets you craft gear with customized stat boosts using Special Leather. Choose which stats to target, and see your odds of success before crafting. Tailoring has": "裁缝允许你使用特殊皮革制作带有自定义属性加成的装备。你可以选择要强化的属性，并在制作前查看成功率。裁缝系统拥有",
    "soft caps and diminishing returns": "软上限与收益递减机制",
    ": the higher a tailored stat is, the smaller each new bonus becomes. Because of that,": "：某项属性已加成的数值越高，每次新增的加成就会越少。正因如此，",
    "small, repeated upgrades": "少量多次的升级",
    "can sometimes shape a piece better than spending everything at once. A piece’s": "有时比一次性投入所有资源更能塑造出一件好装备。装备的",
    "rarity": "稀有度",
    "is determined when it is first crafted and is": "在首次制作时确定，并且",
    "purely cosmetic": "仅有外观差异",
    ". But of course we know you care about that.": "——不过我们当然知道你在意这个。",

    "Rewards": "奖励",

