    "Equip gear or passives that grant Mining Bonus.": "带上可以提供采矿加成的装备或被动技能。",
    // "The dwarves of Mist might provide gear, but they seem to be obsessed with Death Quests lately.": "迷雾镇的矮人或许能提供装备，但他们最近似乎对死亡任务着迷。",
    "A pickaxe and skill is a good start, but the mining helmet you need is being held as a bounty reward by the Carcass Stacker, you will need to defeat the Trolls of the Troll Hole fifty times.": "铁镐和矿工技能是个不错的开始，但你需要的矿工头盔正作为赏金奖励在堆尸者·斯塔克手上，你需要击败巨魔洞穴的巨魔 50 次。",
    "You probably aren't strong enough to do that, and you should give up on everything.": "以你这点实力，还是算了吧，什么都别想了。",
    "This place only yields to those who have rewritten enough timelines.": "此地只向那些已经重写过足够多时间线的人敞开。",
    "Complete more New Game+ runs.": "完成更多次 New Game+ 通关。",
    "Each completed reweaving strengthens your claim on impossible places.": "你每完成一次重编写，就离那些“不可能之地”更近一步。",
    "Some doors do not open to power alone.": "有些门不是靠力量就能打开。",
    "This place recognizes only a specific path.": "此地只认一条特定的道路。",
    "The True Viable Path": "真正可行之路",
    "Your prior choices must align with this area鈥檚 expectations.": "你之前的所有选择都必须符合此区域对你的期待。",
    "The Country Club is very particular about who it considers viable.": "乡村俱乐部对“可行”的标准极其苛刻。",
    "The Country Club expects proper regalia. Standards, my dear visitor, Standards.": "乡村俱乐部要求得体的盛装。标准，我亲爱的访客，标准。",
    "Requires no gear equipped to enter.": "卸下所有装备才能进入。",
    "Remove all equipment and try again.": "请卸下所有装备再试一次。",
    "Unequip every slot (weapon, armor, accessories, etc.).": "卸下所有物品（武器、护甲、饰品等等）。",
    "This place rejects artifacts. Flesh only.": "此地排斥人造物品。只接受血肉之躯。",
    "Entry blocked by job requirements.": "由于未满足职业要求，你无法进入。",
    "Forge more golems in the Workshop.": "在工坊里铸造更多魔像。",
    "Assign more combat specializations to your golems.": "分配更多的战斗魔像。",
    "Tackle easier content first to build up your warband before marching in here.": "先从简单的关卡开始，建立你的军团，壮大你的队伍，然后再进军此处。",
    "Scrap some golems at the Workshop to reduce your numbers.": "在工坊中拆解一些魔像以减少数量。",
    "Or consider sending a smaller Officer strike team instead of your full army.": "考虑派出一支较小的军官突击队，而非你的所有部队。",
    "This region is unstable; large forces are more liability than asset here.": "此区域不稳定；大规模部队在此处弊大于利。",
    "complete": "完成",
    "start": "开始",
    "finish it": "完成任务",
    "begin it": "开始任务",
