    "Stats are only gained when leveling up. You can reset your character level by donating XP at temples.": "只有在升级时才能获得属性。你可以通过在圣殿奉献经验值来重置角色等级。",
    "Enemy Resonance": "敌人共鸣",
    "Shadow Dart": "暗影飞镖",
    "Bullseye?  Someone's eye anyway.": "正中靶心？反正打中了某人的眼睛。",
    "Shadow Knife": "暗影之刃",
    "A blade from the dark. It strikes with the power of your shadow.": "一柄来自黑暗的刀刃。它以你暗影的力量出击。",
    "Finale": "终曲",
    "A grand finale of music and magic. The culmination of your performance.": "一场音乐与魔法的盛大终章。你表演的巅峰。",
    "Acid Splash": "酸液溅射",
    "A small splash of acid. Not very impressive, but it gets the job done.": "一小片酸液溅射。效果不算太好，但也能完成任务。",
    "Explosive Cocktail": "爆炸鸡尾酒",
    "Shaken, not stirred.": "摇匀，不要搅拌。",
    "Tax Time": "征税时刻",
    "You demand a tax from your enemies. In blood and gold.": "你向敌人征税。以鲜血和金币。",
    "Weight Swing": "全力挥击",
    "You swing your weight around, gets the job done though.": "你利用你的体重全力挥出一击——虽然姿势不雅，但确实管用。",
    "Chi Strike": "气劲打击",
    "There is a snake in your heart, and it strikes with the power of your chi.  It also heals you a little bit, because balance and all that.": "你心中有一条蛇，它携着你的气劲之力出击。同时为你恢复少许生命，毕竟要讲究什么平衡之类的。",
    "Soul Bomb": "灵魂炸弹",
    "There is a bright light in the stillness of your soul. You release it in a burst of energy.": "你灵魂的寂静之中有一道明亮的光。你将它化作一股能量爆发释放出来。",
    "Murmur": "低语",
    "You quietly mumble something religious. It doesn't sound like much, but it's annyoing enough to hurt.": "你低声嘟囔了几句宗教用语。听起来没什么了不起——但足够烦人，以至于能造成伤害。",
    "Preach": "说教",
    "Your self-righteous sermon is pain to listen to, except for you.": "你那自以为是的说教，除了你自己，别人听着都难受。",
    "Hallelujah": "哈利路亚",
    "I couldn't feel, so I tried to touch": "我无法感受，于是我试着去触碰",
    "Coin Trick": "硬币戏法",
    "The damage is just a side effect of forcibly removing coins.  Too bad it's not very many coins.": "造成的伤害只是强行取出金币的一个副作用。可惜钱并不多。",
    "Coin Trap": "硬币陷阱",
    "The damage is just a side effect of forcibly removing coins.": "造成的伤害只是强行取出金币的一个副作用。",
    "Surge": "涌动",
    "Unleash a surge of pure willpower.": "释放一股纯粹的意志之力。",
    "Anti-Magic Bomb": "反魔法炸弹",
    "Pretty hypocritical using magic to cast an anti-magic bomb.": "用魔法来施放反魔法炸弹，可真是够虚伪的。",
    "Ember": "余烬",
    "A small burst of fire. Not very impressive.": "一小股火焰爆发。不算很壮观。",
    "Fireball": "火球术",
    "You didn't ask how big the room was, did you?": "你没问这个房间有多大，对吧？",
    "Meteor": "陨石术",
    "Meteor. The very best there is. When you absolutely, positively got to kill every enemy in the room, accept no substitutes.": "陨石。最顶尖的存在。当你绝对、肯定要杀死房间里每一个敌人的时候，没有比这个更好的选择。",
    "Accountant": "会计",
    "Masters of numbers and ledgers, Accountants ensure the financial health of organizations through meticulous record-keeping and analysis.": "会计是精通数字与账目的大师，通过细致的记录与分析确保组织的财务健康。",
    "Determinist": "决定论者",
    "A Determinist believes that all events, including moral choices, are determined completely by previously existing causes.": "决定论者相信，所有事件——包括道德选择——都完全由先前存在的因果决定。",
    "Diplomat": "外交官",
    "Skilled in negotiation and cultural understanding, Diplomats unlock special interactions with Town Leaders.": "外交官精通谈判与文化理解，能解锁与城镇领袖的特殊互动。",
    "Flesh Merchant": "血肉商贩",
    "Handles the kind of procurement you never ask too many questions about.\nConverts obscene amounts of gold into fresh Blank Golems.": "处理那种你从不会多问来源的采购。\n将天文数字的金币转化为新鲜的空白魔像。",
    "Fleshsmith": "血肉塑形师",
    "Converts one’s own flesh into obedient homunculi.  That which does not kill me, multiplies me.": "将自身的血肉转化为顺从的造物。凡不能杀死我的，必使我繁衍增多。",
    "Assassin": "刺客",
    "A killer in the shadows. Strikes swiftly and vanishes before retaliation.": "暗影中的杀手。出手迅捷，在反击到来之前便已消失无踪。",
    "Ghost": "幽灵",
    "Reaper": "收割者",
