    "Tailor": "裁缝",
    "Tailor makes special Head, Body, and Leg gear.  Out of very Special Leather.": "裁缝能用特殊的皮革制作特殊的头部、躯干和腿部装备。",
    "Angler": "垂钓者",
    "Catches fish at lakes. Gains AP from fishing, not battle.": "在湖泊钓鱼。从垂钓而非战斗中获得技能点。",
    "Forester": "护林员",
    "Harvests wood and maintains the forest. Gains AP from gathering, not battle.": "收获木材并维护森林。从采集而非战斗中获得技能点。",
    "Miner": "矿工",
    "Mycologist": "真菌学者",
    "Hunts down and harvests wild mycelium to repair ruined soil.": "追猎并采集野生菌丝，以修复受损的土壤。",
    "Philosopher": "哲学家",
    "Says nothing with the most words posssible.": "用最多的辞藻说着最少的内容。",
    "Scrounger": "拾荒者",
    "“Blessed are the resourceful, for they shall glean from the overlooked and inherit the bounty of need.”": "“机敏者受福，因他们将从不被留意之处拾取所需，并承继匮乏中的丰饶。”",
