    "Will murder change anything, probably not.  But it sure is fun.": "谋杀能改变什么吗？大概不能。但确实挺有意思。",
    "Why would anyone make a fake pony?  I suppose for like a carnival or something. But this is a REAL pony.  It just wants to trample you to death.": "为什么会有人做一匹假小马？我猜是为了嘉年华之类的吧。但这是一匹真正的小马。它只想把你踩死。",
    "Why are you going around smashing statues? They didn't do anything to you.": "你为什么到处砸雕像？它们又没惹你。",
    "Who is dreaming this?": "是谁在做这个梦？",
    "Whiteout Whinny": "雪盲嘶鸣",
    "Whipping Branches": "鞭打枝条",
    "Where you going to run to?": "你要逃到哪里去？",
    "Where you going to hide.": "你要藏到哪里去。",
    "Where have all the real wolves gone?": "真正的狼都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real vipers gone?": "真正的毒蛇都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real spiders gone?": "真正的蜘蛛都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real ravens gone?": "真正的渡鸦都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real owls gone?": "真正的猫头鹰都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real hounds gone?": "真正的猎犬都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real elephants gone?": "真正的大象都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real bears gone?": "真正的熊都去哪儿了？",
    "Where have all the real badgers gone?": "真正的獾都去哪儿了？",
    "When you see them, side by side, the fact that the other was a pony is more obvious.  This one is tall.": "当你把它们并排放着看时，另一只是小马的事实就更明显了。这一只很高。",
    "What's the difference between a hitman and an assassin?  Professionalism. Price.  It doesn't matter, you'll kill them all the same.": "杀手和刺客有什么区别？专业素养。价格。无所谓——反正你都会杀了他们。",
    "What's going on with these things?  Why do they walk in circles?  Why do they attack you on sight?": "这些东西是怎么回事？为什么它们绕圈走？为什么一见到你就攻击？",
    "What makes the grass grow?  Blood.": "是什么让草生长？血。",
    "What kind of mage carries a firearm?  The Church is clearly not interested in tradition.": "什么样的法师会携带枪械？教会显然对传统不感兴趣。",
    "What is this, a bullet factory?": "这是什么——子弹工厂吗？",
    "What did you let wither away to buy this mercy?": "你让什么凋零了，才换来这份仁慈？",
    "What choices have you made to believe that fighting her is a good idea?": "你做了什么选择，才会觉得与她战斗是个好主意？",
    "What an angry bird.  It seems like it's more interested in eating your most precious memories than your flesh.": "多么暴戾的凶鸟。比起血肉，它更渴望吞噬你珍贵的记忆。",
    "What all does it snap at? Everything, apparently.  It's also faster than you would think.": "它什么都咬？显然什么都咬。而且比你想的要快。",
    "What a cute little dragon! Very little, in fact kind of ridiculously small.": "多可爱的小龙啊！非常小——事实上，小得有点离谱了。",
