    "Sometimes you just die.": "有时候你就是会死。",
    "Something tumbles out of the man's hat.  He picks it up off the ground and you hear crunching sounds.": "有什么东西从那个人的帽子里掉了出来。他从地上捡起——你听到了嘎吱嘎吱的咀嚼声。",
    "Something sinister's not going to build itself, you know.": "邪恶之物可不会自己冒出来，你懂的。",
    "Something immense finally decides to stop moving.": "某个巨物终于决定不再前行。",
    "Something follows just outside your shadow, striking only when you move. The heat builds with every step you take.": "有什么东西紧贴在你的影子之外，只有在你移动时才会发起攻击。每走一步，热度便攀升一分。",
    "Somehow, this rabbit is real. You've fought \"rabbits\" before, but you can clearly see the difference.  Somehow, this one is alive. Being around it, you feel so much weaker and more aware of what you actually are.": "不知怎么的，这只野兔是真实的。你以前也打过“野兔”——但你能清楚地看出区别。不知怎么的，这一只是活的。待在它身边，你感觉自己虚弱得多，也更清楚地意识到自己到底是什么。",
    "Some people seem incapable of being alone with their thoughts.  They bring boomboxes on hikes and blast music for everyone to hear.  This hiker is one of those people.": "有些人似乎无法独处。他们徒步时带着手提音箱，把音乐放给所有人听。这个徒步者就是那种人。",
