    "Knotted muscle beneath slick skin, simple, brutal, inevitable.": "光滑皮肤下紧绷的肌肉，简单、残酷、不可阻挡。",
    "Kindness Wins": "善良获胜",
    "Killing Brush": "致命刷扫",
    "Kick to the Head": "踢头",
    "Just a little pinprick... There'll be no more... But you may feel a little sick": "只是轻轻扎一下……很快就没事了……但你可能会有轻微的不适",
    "Judgmental Stare": "审判凝视",
    "It's not not an ant.": "它并非不是蚂蚁。",
    "It's hard to see, but you can make out the shape of a giant humanoid figure looming in the distance. It has six wings, and it's covered in golden feathers. It's the size of a skyscraper.  It also seems to be part of a legion of similar figures.": "很难看清——但你能辨认出一个巨大的人形轮廓在远处若隐若现。它有六只翅膀，覆满金色羽毛。它有一座摩天大楼那么大。而且它似乎也是一支类似军团中的一员。",
    "It's full of goo.": "它里面全是粘液。",
    "It watches you watching it. The line between the two begins to blur.": "它注视着你注视它。两者之间的界限开始模糊。",
    "It watched your every step. Now it pounces.": "它注视了你的每一步。现在它扑过来了。",
    "It unknots, slowly—like a decision finally released.": "它缓缓地松解——像一个终于被放下的决定。",
    "It stops being not quite a thing and becomes a thing you survived.": "它不再是某种模棱两可之物，而是成为了你亲历的一段过往。",
    "It seems to be gathering the hay. It seems like if you were a farmer, you might have something to say about that.": "它似乎在收集干草。如果你是个农夫，你大概会对这件事有话要说。",
    "It seems like if you were an expert in murder, you might be able to relate to this evil, very real, spider.": "如果你是个谋杀专家，你大概能理解这只邪恶而非常真实的蜘蛛。",
    "It perches in perfect stillness, head cocked like it's listening to your balance sheet. Every blink sounds like a stamp of approval or a rejection.": "它完美地静止栖息着，头歪向一边——像是在听你的资产负债表。每一次眨眼都像是一个“批准”或“拒绝”的盖章声。",
    "It must have been left here by the previous farmer.": "一定是前一个农夫留下的。",
    "It moves through the corn like a whisper. You don’t see it until the stalks bend wrong.": "它在玉米地里移动，像一阵轻语。你看不见它直到玉米秆弯曲变形。",
    "It moves a half-step out of sync with you, as if remembering every road you never took.": "它总是与你错开半步，仿佛记得所有你从未走过的路。",
    "It looks like a regular troll, but its skin is made of coal. It radiates an intense heat that can melt steel.": "它看起来像一只普通的巨魔——但它的皮肤由煤炭构成。它散发着足以熔化钢铁的炽热高温。",
    "It jiggles with frost. You can see your breath.": "它随着寒气微微颤动。你能看见自己呼出的白雾。",
    "It is small. It is angry. It does not hesitate, flinch, or flee. You get the sense it has killed much larger things than you.": "它很小。它很愤怒。它不犹豫、不退缩、不逃跑。你有一种感觉——它杀死过比你大得多的东西。",
    "It is a bank, frozen in time, and frozen in ice.": "那是一座银行，凝固于时间，封存于寒冰。",
    "It gallops on splintered limbs of rotting timber, each step driving jagged, rusted nails deeper into the ground.": "它以腐朽木料制成的裂肢奔腾驰骋，每一步都将锈蚀的锯齿铁钉更深地楔入大地。",
    "It doesn't matter how many they send at you, it doesn't matter that they know you're coming.": "不管他们派多少人来对付你——不管他们知道你会来，都无所谓。",
    "It doesn't matter how many seals they carry, it doesn't matter that they filed the warrant in triplicate. They came to end your miracles. Quietly, professionally.": "不管他们携带了多少封印——不管他们把令状一式三份归档了，都无所谓。他们是来终结你的奇迹的。悄无声息地、专业地。",
    "It doesn't matter how many contracts they burn, it doesn't matter how many times they write your name. These people probably have a cool back story and everything. You don't care.  You're just trying to survive.  You're just seeking what?  Justice?  Revenge?": "不管他们烧了多少契约——不管他们写下你的名字多少次。这些人大概有很酷的背景故事什么的。你不在乎。你只是想在活下去。你在寻求什么？正义？复仇？",
    "It does not walk. It simply appears. Cold and ancient and filled with judgment.  It looks vaguely delicious, maybe an expert Chef could learn a recipe.": "它不是走过来的。它就这么出现了。冰冷、古老、充满审判。它看起来隐约很美味——也许一个专业的厨师能从中学到一道菜谱。",
    "It does not rush. It simply arrives when it is time.": "它不急不躁，时机一到，它便会到来。",
    "It decomposes you on principle.": "它分解你是出于它的原则。",
    "It darts from dark water, all speed and impact.": "它从黑暗的水中疾驰而出，速度极快，冲击力十足。",
    "It coils in the eddies, striking faster than the eye can follow.": "它在漩涡中盘旋，攻击速度之快，令人目不暇接。",
    "It carves ripples through the current, striking with unnerving precision.": "它划过水流，刻出涟漪——以令人不安的精准发起攻击。",
    "It cannot be reasoned with. It cannot be bribed. It simply continues, until you stop.": "它无法被说动，无法被收买。它只是继续运行，直到你停下来。",
    "Is the dungeon itself attacking you?": "地牢本身在攻击你吗？",
    "Is that rhino some sort of police officer for railways?  You better hope you don't have any contraband chemicals on you.": "那头犀牛是某种铁路警察吗？你最好希望自己身上没带违禁化学药品。",
    "Is that a Wraith or a Slime? Yes.": "那是恶灵还是史莱姆？都是。",
