    "In the West it seems like things simply seem, they aren't exactly. This is hypothetically the leader of a pack of Wolves.": "在西方，事物似乎只是“看似”——并不完全确切。这头狼在假设上是狼群的首领。",
    "In the West it seems like things simply seem, they aren't exactly. This is hypothetically a Wolf.": "在西方，事物似乎只是“看似”——并不完全确切。这头狼在假设上是一只狼。",
    "Immutable High Priest": "恒常大祭司",
    "If two bodies exert forces on each other, the forces have the same magnitude but opposite directions.": "如果两个物体相互施加力——这些力大小相等、方向相反。",
    "Icy Jab": "冰寒刺击",
    "Ice Slime": "冰霜史莱姆",
    "I think they fell into a bad crowd.  There it is, behind them.": "我觉得它们跟错了人。它在它们后面——就在那里。",
    "I don't think they wanted to work here, I don't think they wanted to try and sell you stuff either, but corporate says you have to be enthusiastic about the products, so here we are.": "我不觉得他们想在这里工作，也不觉得他们想向你推销任何东西。但公司说了，对产品必须有热情——所以，就这样吧。",
    "I don't know who these trees think they are, standing there in the swamp like they own the place. Obviously they don't pay taxes.": "我不知道这些树以为自己是谁，站在沼泽里跟自己家里似的。显然，它们不交税。",
