    "Hopefully you're not trying to steal anything. It's funny how much more terrifying a dog can be compared to a wolf. It must be that little bit of human cruelty that makes all the difference.": "希望你不是在偷东西。有趣的是——狗可以比狼可怕得多。一定是那一丁点人类残忍的成分造就了这种差别。",
    "Hopefully your mind is calm and still.  What was it you were supposed to do in a bear attack?  Oh right, play dead.  Just... don't move.  Well, you won't have to play for long.": "希望你的心灵平静而安宁。在熊攻击时你应该做什么来着？对了——装死。只是……别动。好吧——你其实不用装太久。",
    "Hopefully you are an expert in poisons and perhaps antipoison?  This viper is definitely real, and very dangerous.": "希望你是个毒药专家——也许还有解毒专家？这条蝰蛇绝对是真的，而且非常危险。",
