    "Hoard Communion": "集群共鸣",
    "Hmm, apparently you're not on the list.  Sorry, buddy, but Church protocol is clear: no unauthorized personnel allowed beyond this point.  And apparently they hired dragons to enforce it.": "嗯——看来你不在名单上。抱歉了，伙计——教会的规定很明确：未经授权的人员不得越过此点。而且他们似乎雇了龙来执行这一点。",
    "Hitman": "杀手",
    "Hiking Club": "徒步俱乐部",
    "Hexmark Bloom": "咒印绽放",
    "He's not waiting anymore.": "他不再等待了。",
    "He's going to get swamp water all over his nice suit.  Not very professional.": "他那一身好西装全都会溅上沼泽水。不太专业。",
    "He's a lumberjack, and he's okay.  He sleeps all night and he works all day.": "他是个伐木工，日子还算不赖。整夜安睡，整日劳作。",
    "Her love is as deep as your wanting.": "她的爱如你的渴望一样深。",
    "Her love for you is boundless, but her methods are... unorthodox.": "她对你的爱是无边的——但她的方式……不太寻常。",
    "Her hatred is as sharp as your pulse.": "她的恨如你的脉搏一样锋利。",
    "Her hatred is as pure and deep as the snow.": "她的恨如雪一般纯净而深沉。",
    "Her feathers scatter. The cliffs fall silent.": "她的羽毛散落。悬崖归于寂静。",
    "Hemorrhage Horse": "溢血之马",
    "Hellfire has condensed into equine form, it retains its judgement.": "地狱之火凝聚成马形——它保留着审判之力。",
    "Heavy Swing": "沉重挥击",
    "Heavy magic burst with limited charges.": "重型魔法爆发，有使用次数限制。",
    "Heavy magic burst (reduced by MDEF) with limited charges.": "重型魔法爆发（受魔法防御减免），有使用次数限制。",
    "Heart Swamp Shadow": "沼泽之心暗影",
    "He’s been fishing here since before anyone started writing down who owned what. Now he’s the kind of “owner” that floats, stares, and collects.": "在有人开始记录“谁拥有什么”之前，他就已经在这儿钓鱼了。如今他是那种“漂浮、凝视、然后收割”的“主人”。",
    "He whacks you with his cane.  Apparently it's a magic cane.": "他用拐杖敲了你一下。显然那是一根魔法拐杖。",
    "He was a farmer once. Or perhaps he still is. The corn whispers his name.": "他曾经是个农夫——又或者他仍然是。玉米低语着他的名字。",
    "He seems to think he has something for you to sign. You are increasingly unsure that you still have hands.": "他似乎觉得自己有什么东西要让你签字。你越来越不确定自己还有没有手。",
    "He seems to have decided.": "他似乎已经决定了。",
    "He just wants to buy you a drink and talk about how cool he is.  Those stories seem practiced.": "他只是想请你喝一杯，然后聊聊他有多酷。那些故事听起来像是排练过的。",
    "He is ancient and withered, with tears streaming down his face.  He clutches a small, shining object in his hands.": "他古老而干枯，泪水顺着脸颊流下。他紧紧攥着一件闪闪发光的小东西。",
    "He doesn't even seem to be noticing the water filling his lungs.  He does seem interested in putting more water into your lungs, though.": "他似乎根本不在意水灌满了他的肺——但他似乎很有兴趣往你的肺里灌更多水。",
    "He doesn't do much but he keeps standing.  He always keeps standing.": "他做的不多——但他一直站着。他总是站着。",
