    "Based on the rest of his outfit, you would expect him to carry a halberd or something, but instead he wields what appears to be a machine gun. Or maybe it's an assault rifle?  You're not sure.": "根据他身上的其他装束，你大概会以为他扛着一把戟之类的——但他拿着的却是一把机枪。又或者是突击步枪？你不太确定。",
