    "As the Pontifical Mage falls, he utters a final transmission into his radio, calling for backup.  You can almost hear the crackle of static as reinforcements are summoned to the fight.": "当教宗法师倒下时，他向电台发出了最后的通讯，呼叫支援。你几乎可以听到增援被召唤时电流的噼啪声。",
    "As the Pontifical Guard falls, he utters a final transmission into his radio, calling for backup.  You can almost hear the crackle of static as reinforcements are summoned to the fight.": "当教宗卫兵倒下时，他向电台发出了最后的通讯，呼叫支援。你几乎可以听到增援被召唤时电流的噼啪声。",
