    "Approaching the End": "接近终点",
    "Apprentice Witch": "学徒女巫",
    "Apparently you're committed to the destruction of art.  I see how it is.": "显然你铁了心要毁掉这件艺术品。行，我懂了。",
    "Apparently there is always a bigger fish.  Hopefully you're an expert in dealing with fish-related problems.": "看来总有更大的鱼等着你。希望你是一位处理鱼类相关问题的专家。",
    "Apparently there is a price on your head?  That's not good.": "显然你头上被挂了赏金？那可不太妙。",
    "Antler Bash": "鹿角猛击",
    "Antiseptic Spore": "防腐孢子",
    "Antiphonal Priest": "对唱祭司",
    "Antiphon": "对唱",
    "AntiAnt": "反蚂蚁",
    "Another Cosmic Postman arrives, as if your nonexistence required a signature.": "又一位宇宙邮递员到了——仿佛你的不存在需要有人签收确认。",
    "Angle-Slip Whisper": "倾角低语",
    "And why won’t it let you wake up?": "为什么它不让你醒来？",
    "An unstoppable wall of law and punishment.": "一堵不可阻挡的法律与惩罚之墙。",
    "Alligator": "短吻鳄",
    "Allergic Reaction": "过敏反应",
